FBIS3-30975 "dreeu030_p_94012" FBIS-EEU-94-030 Document Type:Daily Report 14 Feb 1994 POLAND IMF Conditions Fulfilled for Debt Reduction LD0902192294 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1800 GMT 9 Feb 94 LD0902192294 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network Language: Polish Article Type:BFN [Text] According to initial data for 1994, Poland has fulfilled the standby agreement reached in November 1992 with the IMF. The fulfillment of this agreement is a condition for a 20-percent reduction--that is. about $8 billion in government debts to the states who are our creditors grouped in the Paris Club. The club is to make a decision on this matter at the beginning of April.
